<paragraph blockId="4.[751,1337,2304,2684]" pageId="4" pageNumber="623">The Asian Badger has been considered conspecific with the European Badger by some authors, but is listed here as a distinct species. Two subspecies are recognized.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
